is what one to two meters

00:06:33.386 --> 00:06:36.362
of sea level rise looks
like in the Mekong Delta.

00:06:36.386 --> 00:06:39.013
That's where half
of Vietnam's rice is grown.

00:06:39.037 --> 00:06:42.146
Infrastructure is going to be affected.

00:06:42.170 --> 00:06:44.666
Airports around the world
are located on the coast.

00:06:44.690 --> 00:06:46.690
It makes sense, right? There's open space,

00:06:46.714 --> 00:06:49.335
the planes can take off and land
without worrying about

00:06:49.359 --> 00:06:51.550
creating noise or avoiding tall buildings.

00:06:51.574 --> 00:06:54.686
Here's just one example,
San Francisco Airport,

00:06:54.710 --> 00:06:57.400
